						<div class="postbody">I'm pretty new to this as well, and I don't know much about music theory, so my methods are pretty weird. To get the basic melody I keep whistling until something "decent" comes out. I record that and run through a note recognition software to get the notes. This is all I've done so far, but I plan to build the rest around the basic melody.</div>

