			<td valign="top">
				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">AKoff Music Composer 2.0 is pretty small and has given me the best results so far. It will create a mid file from wav or direct mic input. I usually whistle and have it convert in real time.
<br />
<br />Then I open the mid in an editor (Anvil Studio, I think) to fix up some notes and tweak the melody a bit and finally get the names and durations of the notes.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

